        <p>Families in the rural communities we work with in India can’t meet basic needs from farming.  Many people migrate to the cities and some even commit suicide.  The situation is tough, but there is hope.  And we’re a part of it.  We create economic opportunities by giving farmers and women’s groups tools to effectively harvest, paying well-above market rates and spreading the word about Garcinia to increase the demand. </p>

        <h3>Spreading love, gratitude and compassion</h3>
        <p>In addition to our efforts in India, we’re promoting balance and spreading love, compassion and gratitude through Sant Sessions.  We’ve got some other things in the works too ;).</p>
